author: The Current
description:
Minnesota musician John Munson reflects on his recovery after suffering a stroke last winter. We are thankful he’s doing much better.

You can catch The New Standards live for their upcoming Holiday Shows at The State Theatre in Minneapolis Dec. 5 & 6.
